<script type="text/javascript">
	(function($) {
		var parent;
		var menu = $('.menu');
		var over = 0;
		menu.find('.dt').bind('mouseover', function(e) {
			e.preventDefault();
			menu.find('dd').css('display', 'none');
			if (over > 0) {
				over = 0;
			} else {
				$(this).parent().find('dd').css('display', 'block');
				over++;
			}
		});
		
		menu.find('.dt').bind('mouseout', function(e) {
			if (over > 0) {
				over = 0;
			} 
			setTimeout(function() { if (over == 0) menu.find('dd').css('display', 'none'); }, 0);
		});
		
		menu.find('dd').bind('mouseover', function(e) {
			over++;
			parent = $(this).parent().addClass('active');
		});
		
		menu.find('dd').bind('mouseout', function(e) {
			parent = $(this).parent()[0];
			if (over > 0) {
				over = 0;
			} 
			$(this).parent().removeClass('active');
			setTimeout(function() { if (over == 0) menu.find('dd').css('display', 'none'); }, 0);
		});
	})(jQuery);
</script>

	var showsSlider_video_template = "<div class=\"showsSlider_video\">\n\t<video id=\"!!id!!\" controls=\"controls\" width=\"640\" height=\"510\" poster=\"!!filename!!.jpg\" style=\"display: inline-block; width: 640px; height: 510px; background-color: #F8F8FF;\">\n\t\t<source src=\"!!filename!!.mp4\" type=\"video\/mp4\" data-ext=\"mp4\" \/>\n\t\t<source src=\"!!filename!!.ogg\" type=\"video\/ogg\" data-ext=\"ogg\" \/>\n\t\t<a href=\"!!filename!!.mp4\"><img style=\"display: block;\" border=\"0\" src=\"!!filename!!.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"510\" \/><\/a>\n\t<\/video>\n<\/div>\n";
	
	var showsContainers = [];
	
	var titleContainer = $('.infoZoneBottom h2');
	var subheadlineContainer = $('.infoZoneBottom h3');
	var performancesContainer = $('.infoZoneBottom .performances');
	
	var pause = false;
	var skip = false;
	
	function playShowVideo(index) {
		var id = 'show_video_' + index;
		var filename = shows[index].video.filename;
		var flv = shows[index].video.flv;
		var flash_jpg = shows[index].video.flash_jpg;
		var showsSlider_video = showsSlider_video_template.replace(/!!id!!/g, id).replace(/!!filename!!/g, filename);
			
		var video = jQuery(showsSlider_video).dialog({
			width: 640,
			height: 545,
			draggable: false,
			show: 'fade',
			hide: 'fade',
			modal: true,
			title: shows[index].name,
			open: function() {
				pause = true;
			},
			close: function() {
				pause = false;
				video.remove();
			}
		});
		
		if (navigator.userAgent.match(/3_2 like Mac OS/)) document.getElementById(id).poster = false;
		swfobject.embedSWF(
			'/flash/player.swf',
			id,
			640,
			510,
			'9.0.0',
			'',
			{
				file: flv,
				image: flash_jpg,
				provider: 'video',
				dock: true,
				stretching: 'uniform',
				smoothing: true,
				autostart: true
			},
			{
				menu: "false",
				allowfullscreen: "true",
				allowscriptaccess: "always",
				allownetworking: "always",
				wmode: 'transparent'
			},
			{
				id: 'flash_' + id,
				name: 'flash_' + id
			},
			function(e) {
				if (e.success) {
					if (jQuery !== undefined) {
						jQuery('#flash_!!id!!').parent().children().not('object').remove();
					}
				}
			}
		);
	}
	
	$('.showsSlider').find('.play_button').bind('click', function(e) {
		playShowVideo(0);
		e.preventDefault();
		return false;
	});
	
	function showShowInfo(show, container) {
		titleContainer.html(show.name);
		subheadlineContainer.html(show.subheadline);
		performancesContainer.empty();
		for (var i = 0; i < show.performances.length; i++) {
			var performance = show.performances[i];
			performancesContainer.append('<div class="performance">' + performance.date + '<br /><div class="infoButton lightButton"><a href="' + show.link + '">INFO</a></div>' + (typeof performance.ticketLink === 'undefined' || performance.ticketLink === false ? '' : '<div class="buyTicketsButton lightButton"><a href="' + performance.ticketLink + '" target="_blank">Buy Tickets</a></div>') + '<div style="clear: both;"></div></div>');
		}
		container.find('.play_button').remove();
		if (show.video) {
			var play_button = $('<a href="javascript:void" class="play_button" title="Play Video"></a>');
			container.prepend(play_button);
			play_button.bind('click', function(e) {
				playShowVideo(show.index);
				e.preventDefault();
				return false;
			});
		}
	}
	
	function showShowImage(show, container) {
		container.find('.show_image').attr('src', '');
		container.find('.show_image').attr('src', show.image + '?width=695&height=465&bound=0');
		container.find('.show_image').bind('click', function() {
			window.location.href = show.link;
		});
	}
	
	function dice(image, cols, rows) {
		var diced = $('<div class="diced">');
		var width = image.width();
		var height = image.height();
		var tileWidth = width / cols;
		var tileHeight = height / rows;
		diced.css({
			'width': width + 1,
			'height': height,
			'overflow': 'hidden'
		});
		
		var row;
		var col;
		var tile;
		for (row = 0; row < rows; row++) {
			for (col = 0; col < cols; col++) {
				tile = $('<div class="tile">');
				tile.css({
					//'outline': '1px solid red',
					'float': 'left',
					'background-repeat': 'no-repeat',
					'background-image': 'url(' + image.attr('src') + ')',
					'background-position': (-1 * col * tileWidth) + 'px ' + (-1 * row * tileHeight) + 'px',
					'width': tileWidth,
					'height': tileHeight
				});
				diced.append(tile);
			}
		}
		diced.insertBefore(image);
		return diced;
	}
	
	var i = 0;
	
	showsContainers[i] = $('.showsSlider');
	showShowImage(shows[i], showsContainers[i]);
	
	var current = showsContainers[i];
	var image = null;
	var last = null;
	var diced = null;
	var thumbnails = $('.showsSlider_container .thumbnails');
	var thumbnails_scroller = thumbnails.find('.thumbnails_scroller');
	
	function slide() {
		if (skip) {
			skip = false;
			return;
		}
		if (pause) return;
		
		setTimeout(showNext, 350);
		load(i);
		
		next = showsContainers[i];
		showShowInfo(shows[i], showsContainers[i]);
		
		if (current.css('display') == 'none') {
			showNext();
		}
		
		if (!$.browser.msie || parseInt($.browser.version, 10) > 7) {
			thumbnails_scroller.animate({ 'margin-left': -1 * (i - 4) * 82 }, 200);
		}
		
		i++;
		if (i == (shows.length)) {
			i = 0;
		} else if (typeof showsContainers[i] === 'undefined') {
			// preload
			load(i);
		}
	};
	
	function showNext() {
		$('.showsSlider_container').append(next);
		
		image = next.find('.show_image');
		
		var imageLoaded = function() {
			var cols = 12;
			var rows = 8;
			diced = dice(image, cols, rows);
			var tiles = diced.find('.tile');
			for (var col = 0; col < cols; col++) {
				for (var row = 0; row < rows; row++) {
					var tileIndex = col * rows + row;
					$(tiles[tileIndex]).css('opacity', Math.random());
				}
			}
			image.hide();
			tiles.animate({ opacity: 1 }, {
				duration: 1000,
				easing: 'linear',
				complete: function() {
					last.remove();
					diced.remove();
					image.show();
				}
			});
		};
		
		if (image[0].complete) {
			imageLoaded();
		} else {
			image.bind('load', imageLoaded);
		}
		
		last = current;
		current = next;
	}
	
	function load(i) {
		showsContainers[i] = current.clone();
		showShowImage(shows[i], showsContainers[i]);
	}
	
	thumbnails.find('.thumbnail').bind('click', function() {
		if (i - 1 != $(this).data('index')) {
			skip = false;
			i = $(this).data('index');
			if (image) image.show();
			if (diced) diced.remove();
			current.stop(true, false);
			current.find('.diced').stop(true, false);
			current.find('.tile').stop(true, false);
			current.find('.show_image').stop(true, false);
			current.find('.show_image').show();
			slide();
		}
		skip = true;
	});
	
	if (shows.length > 0) {
		i++;
		showsContainers[i] = current.clone();
		showShowImage(shows[i], showsContainers[i]);
		setInterval(slide, 7000);
	}
});
</script>

jQuery(document).ready(function($) {
	$(".perfDetailsLayer").mouseenter(function() {
		$(this).find(".upcomingPerformanceDetails").stop(true, false);
		$(this).find(".upcomingPerformanceDetails").animate({ "top": "0" }, "fast");
		$(this).find(".upcomingPerformanceDetails").addClass('active');
	});
	$(".perfDetailsLayer").mouseleave(function() {
		$(this).find(".upcomingPerformanceDetails").stop(true, false);
		$(this).find(".upcomingPerformanceDetails").animate({ "top": "79px" }, "fast");
		$(this).find(".upcomingPerformanceDetails").removeClass('active');
	});
});
</script>
